name: WHERE IS IT? (Julomac12)
description:
It looks like you have lost your key while working in the field with your friend who just saw something through the fog what could it be? The last time you remember seeing your key was when you open the sheep gate, that being said you've also filled some holes in the forest maybe it fell out of your pocket? 

using w, a,s,d, and the mouse explore the map and find your key
